{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol\/getWeekOfYear()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeprotocol\/getweekofyear()"]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"extendedModule":"GLib","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","title":"getWeekOfYear()","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"getWeekOfYear","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"externalID":"s:4GLib16DateTimeProtocolPAAE13getWeekOfYearSiyF"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week number for the week containing "},{"code":"datetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The ISO 8601 week number is the same for every day of the week (from","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Moday through Sunday).  That can produce some unusual results"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(described below)."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getWeekOfYear","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The first week of the year is week 1.  This is the week that contains","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the first Thursday of the year.  Equivalently, this is the first week","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that has more than 4 of its days falling within the calendar year.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The value 0 is never returned by this function.  Days contained"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within a year but occurring before the first ISO 8601 week of that"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"year are considered as being contained in the last week of the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"previous year.  Similarly, the final days of a calendar year may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"considered as being part of the first ISO 8601 week of the next year","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"if 4 or more days of that week are contained within the new year.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTimeProtocol":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDateTime"},{"text":" is a structure that combines a Gregorian date and time","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"into a single structure."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DateTimeProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"DateTimeProtocol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DateTimeProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeprotocol"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTimeProtocol/getWeekOfYear()":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol\/getWeekOfYear()","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeprotocol\/getweekofyear()","role":"symbol","title":"getWeekOfYear()","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week number for the week containing "},{"code":"datetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The ISO 8601 week number is the same for every day of the week (from"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Moday through Sunday).  That can produce some unusual results"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(described below)."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"getWeekOfYear","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"url":"\/documentation\/glib","kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","abstract":[],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","role":"collection"}}}